Subject: [PATCH 11/17] Serialize artwork keywords/emotions/type_of_object as
 {en,fr,nl}
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- keywords: mirrors the description i18n pattern (columns already
  existed, fully populated).
- emotions: new emotions.rs module reads the referential table;
  ResultArtwork.emotions is now translated labels instead of raw
  Plutchik keys. Internal Artwork.emotions (raw string) and
  scoring.rs's matching algorithm are untouched — only the final
  result-shaping step, after scoring/selection, changed.
- type_of_object: new types_of_object.rs module, same treatment;
  internal type_of_object_id usage in scoring.rs untouched.
